    "description": "《这是我的战争：孩子们》<br>DLC收入的10%将捐给专为全球武装冲突地区的儿童提供帮助的慈善机构War Child <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/481090/extras/cbb349c62bb3683687fc5664e3a9e7a8.poster.avif?t=1733932125\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/481090/extras/cbb349c62bb3683687fc5664e3a9e7a8.webm?t=1733932125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/481090/extras/cbb349c62bb3683687fc5664e3a9e7a8.mp4?t=1733932125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《这是我的战争：孩子们》 让玩家以战时儿童的全新视角体验在战争中生存的艰难。在本DLC中，玩家将控制被困在围城的一群成年人和孩子。所有人都必须为了生存而苦苦挣扎。《这是我的战争：孩子们》关注的不仅是战争的残酷现实，还淋漓尽致地刻画了孩子们在战争中表现出的纯真天性。他们会笑、会哭、会玩耍，并以孩子的视角去看世界。除了思考如何让大家生存下去，你还必须唤醒内心的童真，才能懂得如何去保护天真无邪的孩子们。他们的童年和未来就在你的手中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/481090/extras/f86a8858f1537b777ab3c2595e919fae.poster.avif?t=1733932125\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/481090/extras/f86a8858f1537b777ab3c2595e919fae.webm?t=1733932125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/481090/extras/f86a8858f1537b777ab3c2595e919fae.mp4?t=1733932125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>开发者寄语：“我们认为，加入孩子们的视角使得这款游戏的体验更加饱满，这是我们做出的最重要的决定之一。但这也要求我们对战争的受害者表示出最高的敬意。因此，我们去除了无谓的血腥场面。我们想展现的是战争中孩子们的独特视角。” <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/481090/extras/35147669d3b490a1427ee1f0185a19f4.poster.avif?t=1733932125\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a